{"tid":1958590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗區議員 頌栢 - 李煒鋒 Deco Lee 遇藍絲暴徒受襲，施襲者逃入元朗警署！","createTime":"2020-04-04T18:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T18:50:56.000Z","uid":324034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4640c9428e377bd3610c3538523991e462466f","tid":1958590,"uid":324034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:33:49.000Z","msg":"【直播影片截圖】元朗區議員 頌栢 - 李煒鋒 Deco Lee 遇藍絲暴徒受襲，施襲者逃入元朗警署！<br />\n<br />\n藍絲暴徒當時正於元朗懸掛抺黑元朗區議會正、副主席的Banner，遭李煒鋒議員當場撞破。 #抺黑Banner相片請見留言<br />\n#元朗警署是否已經成為藍絲暴徒逃走時第一時間諗到嘅自己友地點<br />\n#如果唔係就快啲拉人啦個施襲者走咗入元朗警署喎<br />\n#片段所見有白衫出嚟迎接<br />\n<br />\n巫啟航 Fleco Mo<br />\n王百羽 Henry - 王伯<br />\n李頌慈 Chris Li - 錦田<br />\n伍軒宏&middot;耀祐 Hysan Ng<br />\n張智陽 Felix Cheung<br />\n已到達元朗報案室陪同李煒鋒議員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1531062487069157&amp;id=431937386981678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1531062487069157%26id%3D431937386981678&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=640b87c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1531062487069157&amp;id=431937386981678</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2b966f49bb36b90c4ccca6f86294f3eff72c86","tid":1958590,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:36:19.000Z","msg":"死左link 仆街"},{"pid":"65ae41fcd44cb45f365ef0a5647ab91a37b124cb","tid":1958590,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:49:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e427f9e3bea745d502993bdcc534d78bede8a9f","tid":1958590,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite